Package libshapedraw.shape

Interface Summary
XrayShape A Shape that supports "xray" rendering: sections of the shape that are occluded by another object can be drawn regardless, using a different color (often the same color with reduced transparency) than non-occluded sections.
 

Class Summary
GLUCylinder Render a GLU (OpenGL Utility Library) cylinder or cone.
GLUDisk Render a GLU (OpenGL Utility Library) disk.
GLUPartialDisk Render a GLU (OpenGL Utility Library) partial disk.
GLUShape Intermediate base class for simple shapes rendered using GLU (OpenGL Utility Library).
GLUSphere Render a GLU (OpenGL Utility Library) sphere.
Shape Generic base class for a renderable object.
WireframeCuboid A wireframe box, orthogonal to the x/y/z axes.
WireframeLine A single line segment, going from point A to point B.
WireframeLines A series of connected line segments.
WireframeLinesBlend A series of connected line segments that smoothly blends from one line style to another along the segments.
WireframeLinesBlendIterable A series of connected line segments that smoothly blends from one line style to another along the segments.
WireframeShape Intermediate base class for shapes that are rendered using lines.
